    public static class WikiRevisionDiffInputFormat.DiffReader
extends WikiRevisionReader<RevisionDiff>
    Read every pairs of consecutive revisions and calculate their diffs using Meyer's alogirthm. Return WikipediaRevisionDiff which, among other fields, emits the list of diff between the two texts
